</taxonomicName>
, does not fit the diagnostic characteristics of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Beier" authorityYear="1954" box="[1168,1324,367,393]" class="Insecta" family="Tettigoniidae" genus="Dasyscelidius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="133" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
